{"tid":2110490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一到六點嚇到叫左出黎","createTime":"2020-07-16T03:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T03:34:09.000Z","uid":257880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01afbee9e58f118e8f0a563f3bca9738c703bac6","tid":2110490,"uid":257880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"一到六點嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我比隻錶佢睇，睇左左枝時針指住六點，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「武漢肺炎殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；武漢肺炎殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停講2盒thx。<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，武漢肺炎真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"361c85591a78cbc1342183c695429835e807a0f4","tid":2110490,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"老細死左咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319905d6d4fae1fa774a0c4d6e21fa1e9e72ab59","tid":2110490,"uid":257880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:18:19.000Z","msg":"永久home office"},{"pid":"8a280209273a79c9da212afdb314e2dec095c698","tid":2110490,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}